short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Unofficial stream assistant for Whatnot streams!

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Allows Whatnot streamers to configure Discord-like slash commands in their streams.

Want to allow your viewers to look up the price of a card without leaving your stream? How about enabling a simple "/rules" command that'll respond with the rules of your game?

This extension is not officially maintained by Whatnot.
